<title>IN THE SWEET BYAND BY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. A hehpihna pakcha'n lasa'i tiu,
 A hehpihna hai thei ngeilo chuh!
 Belam No thah thisan pawtpa chuh,
 Amah I pahchak niu tun ma'n le.

[V2]
 * Dan leh kipak takin,
 Luipi pang hawih takah tuok hitiu. (2)

[V3]
 2. Thisan zalin Pathien changlam ah,
 Kumsawt hinna leh nawpna a um;
 Mitin adi'n hinna tui a luong,
 Zie tui chun Lalpa'n ei sil ina.

[V4]
 3. A hehpih tuhin I teppan ui,
 Amah minin kipah na'n I dim;
 Van I tun tieng bang a um kit dem?
 Belam No thiengtho lasak pih ding.

[V5]
 4. Amah mina I kituok khawm tieng,
 I kumsawt munah ei sawl intin;
 Lawp takin Pa In chuh tung hitiu,
 I kumsawt vangsak na gam a chun.

[V6]
 5. Puonzak nuoi achun I chen lai un,
 I thupi pen &quot;Thienthona&quot; hi hen;
 A khuta Lallukhuk chang hiting,
 A Lal lopina chuh mutai tiu.</lyrics>
</song>